  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Adversary is a truly terrifying creature. Born of demonic heritage and formed entirely of malice filled chakra it cannot be tamed and is an engine of destruction. This Adversary is immune to Social interaction, Cannot have its Chakra molding removed, and can spend <strong>1 tenacity die</strong> to reduces all damage it takes by an amount equal to its level until the end of the current turn.</p><p>For all of its power it is weak to Sealing arts. This creature has vulnerability to jutsu with the Fuinjutsu keyword and cannot spend more than 1 Tenacity die in response to their effects.</p>",
